Package org.missions.objective.action

Interface ActionType

All Superinterfaces:
Category, ObjectiveType
All Known Subinterfaces:
BlockActionType
All Known Implementing Classes:
SpawnBlockActionType
public interface ActionType extends ObjectiveType
An ActionType is something that will occur if the parent is complete. This could be placing a block or entity into the world, or sending the player to another location, etc.
